            "content": "## [Security]\n\n- Access token is stored in n8n's\n  encrypted Credentials, never in\n  the workflow JSON.\n- Exported doc tracking auto-cleans\n  after 30 days.\n- No secrets in code."
          },
          "typeVersion": 1
        }
